# SPDX-License-Identifier: PMPL-1.0-or-later
# =============================================================================
# Burble Trustfile — Integrity and Security Verification
# Voice-first communications platform.
#
# Based on the RSR Trustfile example with Burble-specific additions for:
#   - WebRTC/DTLS security
#   - E2EE (Insertable Streams)
#   - Voice-specific threats (eavesdropping, cloning, impersonation)
#   - Avow consent attestation chains
#   - Vext feed integrity verification
#   - NNTPS transport security
#   - BEAM/OTP distribution security
#   - Media privacy hardening
#
# Author: Jonathan D.A. Jewell <j.d.a.jewell@open.ac.uk>
# =============================================================================

